title: fix webdav support for cherokee
body:
webdav with cherokee is somewhat broken.

i installed oc 4.5.5 with cherokee 1.2.101 everything works on the web client, even android and ios apps work but webdav always refuses to login and the sync client says csync failed at the initial sync.

i stopped cherokee and started apache and then magically it all worked, once initial sync is done with apache it actually works with cherokee except for folders, files do sync but folders won't, i get lots of 404s on my logs and the client says the following:
